genius composer
Wolfgang Amadeus Mozart by
taking apart one

00:35.736 --> 00:37.137 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
of his masterpieces.

00:37.237 --> 00:39.673 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
