slowly back to
life on this third day after the
great blizzard.

01:22.449 --> 01:28.221 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Federal offices remained closed,
but work
crews were out early to clear
more snow, and

01:28.322 --> 01:30.157 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
