into those neighborhoods.

01:57.284 --> 01:59.119 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
CHRISTOPHER GELDART, Director,
D.C. Homeland
Security and Emergency
Management Agency:

01:59.219 --> 02:04.424 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
That operation will continue
through today
and through tonight. We're
monitoring progress

02:04.524 --> 02:08.395 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
