the millions,
we ought to reach within weeks.
We can do

04:26.066 --> 04:35.242 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
it. So, finally, if they lose
this momentum,
I think they will live to regret
it.

04:35.342 --> 04:40.547 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Meanwhile, Syrian
opposition
groups backed by Saudi Arabia
met in Riyadh

04:40.647 --> 04:46.319 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
to decide whether to attend the
peace talks.
