Syrian Kurdish

04:46.419 --> 04:52.626 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
party to participate, despite
opposition from
Turkey, which considers it a
terrorist group.

04:52.726 --> 04:58.932 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
A policeman in Afghanistan shot
dead 10 other
officers late Monday in the
country's latest

04:59.032 --> 05:04.704 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
insider attack. It happened in
the south,
in Uruzgan province, bordering
the Taliban

05:04.804 --> 05:10.677 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
