World War I
memorial has been unveiled in
Washington.

05:45.412 --> 05:51.651 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Artist renderings today show
walls bearing
relief sculptures of soldiers,
with quotations.

05:51.751 --> 06:00.760 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
