the White House
in a small urban park.

06:05.966 --> 06:10.971 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Something old is new again in
the world of
Peter Rabbit. There's word today
that an unpublished

06:11.071 --> 06:16.109 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
story by renowned children's
author Beatrix
Potter is bound for bookstores,
more than

06:16.209 --> 06:18.545 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
