06:18.645 --> 06:21.915 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Sharon Thomas of Independent
Television News
has the story.

06:22.015 --> 06:27.787 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
SHARON THOMAS: "Once upon a
time, there was
a serious, well-behaved young
black cat. It

06:27.887 --> 06:33.526 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
