assured me
that no other cats could compare
with Kitty.

06:33.627 --> 06:38.932 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
The tale of "Kitty-in-Boots"
tells the story
of a well-behaved cat who leads
a double life.

06:39.032 --> 06:46.006 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
