New Jersey. He was best known as
the mafia

07:47.267 --> 07:53.840 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
captain Tessio in "The
Godfather," and as
the sad-sack Detective Fish in
the 1970s TV

07:53.940 --> 07:58.645 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
