offenses.

08:58.405 --> 09:03.777 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
The Department of Justice caps
its use at
two months, rather than a full
year. And the

09:03.877 --> 09:09.482 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
