officers from
using solitary for low-level
infractions.

09:09.582 --> 09:11.317 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
Hari Sreenivasan has our look.

09:11.418 --> 09:14.921 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
HARI SREENIVASAN: The
president's changes
would affect about 10,000
federal inmates

09:15.021 --> 09:16.890 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
