organization covering
the criminal justice system.

10:09.342 --> 10:11.311 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
Maurice, I want to start with
you.

10:11.411 --> 10:15.682 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
One of the critiques here is
that this is
going to affect a very small
population in

10:15.782 --> 10:20.920 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
