large populations
that we have in state prisons.
How significant

10:21.020 --> 10:22.188 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
is this impact going to be?

10:22.288 --> 10:24.123 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
MAURICE CHAMMAH, The Marshall
Project: That's
true.

10:24.224 --> 10:27.827 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
It's kind of hard to tell at
this moment sort
of how widespread it will be.
One of the things

10:27.927 --> 10:33.099 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
