10:59.959 --> 11:02.662 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: Shaka, I'm
sure you're excited
about the president's
announcement today,

11:02.762 --> 11:08.034 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
