term and in
the long term?

11:10.904 --> 11:14.340 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
SHAKA SENGHOR, #Cut50: Well, I'm
super excited
about the president's decision
today, because

11:14.440 --> 11:18.344 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
I know the impact that it is
going to have
on men and women who are
currently in solitary

11:18.444 --> 11:20.580 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
