prison system.

11:20.680 --> 11:26.286 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And for me, personally, knowing
the devastating
impact of being in the most
barbaric and inhumane

11:26.386 --> 11:31.724 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
