hours a day,
and in some cases 24 hours a
day, I just think

11:31.824 --> 11:36.696 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
that it's one of those type of
moments where
it helps people to think about,
you know,

11:36.796 --> 11:41.134 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
what our responsibility is in
terms of men
and women who come home from
prison.

11:41.234 --> 11:44.938 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And we have a choice. We have a
choice whether
we want to bring home healthy
